29:27.099 --> 29:28.476
Ugh!

29:29.602 --> 29:30.686
Will you hurry up?

29:33.439 --> 29:35.900
- Stop! Get back here.

29:39.403 --> 29:40.237
Later, kid.

29:43.240 --> 29:45.743
Now, you're gonna feel
my ninja skills.

29:45.743 --> 29:47.203
