just won't quit.

29:47.203 --> 29:48.454
Oh, that's no kid.

29:50.289 --> 29:52.416
That's some kind
of feral mutant.

29:53.000 --> 29:54.376
Whoa!

29:55.252 --> 29:57.379
Oh, no!
The boss is gonna kill us.

29:57.379 --> 29:59.798
