34:32.070 --> 34:33.489
Ugh! Gross.

34:36.617 --> 34:38.243
<i>You gotta be careful, Damian.</i>

34:39.244 --> 34:42.915
<i>Oh, Alfred,
the diaper's integrity,
it's been compromised.</i>

34:42.915 --> 34:45.501
<i>- I need wipes...</i>
- Ah, Dad.

34:48.253 --> 34:49.963
<i>...and though I'd won
the brutal fight,</i>

34:49.963 --> 34:53.300
<i>the searing pain
