are still with me.</i>

34:53.300 --> 34:54.301
<i>Every day.</i>

34:55.594 --> 34:57.387
<i>Okay, so, onto the Batsuit.</i>

34:57.387 --> 34:58.555
Yeah!

34:58.555 --> 35:02.726
<i>To be honest, Damian,
part of me never wanted you
