35:02.726 --> 35:05.103
<i>But another part of me
always knew deep down</i>

35:05.103 --> 35:07.606
<i>that this is what
you were born to do.</i>

35:07.606 --> 35:11.276
<i>My only regret
is not being by your side
when you did it.</i>

35:11.276 --> 35:14.154
<i>Thankfully, that's where
the suit's tech comes in.</i>

35:14.154 --> 35:18.534
<i>With the help of AI,
