into the suit.</i>

35:18.534 --> 35:20.744
<i>Activating Bat-Dad.</i>

35:30.921 --> 35:32.172
<i>Upload complete.</i>

35:33.382 --> 35:35.551
<i>Okay. Good luck, Damian.</i>

35:35.551 --> 35:38.637
<i>And remember,
