your eye out.

01:22:51.759 --> 01:22:54.595
A Merry Christmas
to me and to you,

01:22:54.595 --> 01:22:56.347
a dark night.

01:22:58.557 --> 01:22:59.892
You missed!

01:23:00.768 --> 01:23:02.687
That's kind of the point.

